Package: torcontroller
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: privoxy(>= 3.0.28), privoxy(<< 3.1),
         procps,
         systemctl (>= 1.4),
         tor(>= 0.4.2.7), tor(<< 0.5),
         iptables,
         sudo,
         ${misc:Depends}
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Description: Torcontroller is a simple controller to switch network to 
  provides a CLI for managing and switching your network through 
  the Tor network. It integrates Tor, Privoxy, and system utilities to help 
  protect your identity and enhance your privacy. Ideal for use in Docker or 
  lightweight environments.
